Generic single-database configuration for Alembic.

RAGNAR migration strategy
-------------------------
* Development (default): ``init_db()`` uses SQLModel ``create_all`` + SQLite
  ALTER backfills. Alembic is optional.
* Production: set ``ENVIRONMENT=production`` (or ``SCHEMA_BOOTSTRAP=alembic``).
  ``create_all`` is disabled. Before starting the app:

      alembic upgrade head

* New schema changes: edit SQLModel models, then:

      alembic revision --autogenerate -m "describe_change"
      alembic upgrade head

Never wipe production data to "fix" schema drift.
